d2-a093-dbba6f686c04','{\"id\": \"a1690e89-c30b-4bd2-a093-dbba6f686c04\", \"slug\": \"about-us\", \"title\": \"About Girik Class – Excellence in Maritime Classification\", \"body_html\": \"<h1>Girik Class: Redefining Maritime Safety</h1><p>Established as a leading <strong>Recognized Organization (RO)</strong>, Girik Class provides comprehensive classification and statutory services to the global maritime industry. Our mission is to safeguard life at sea and protect the marine environment through rigorous technical standards and digital innovation.</p><h3>Our Technical Expertise</h3><p>We operate a dedicated network of highly qualified marine surveyors and technical experts across all major ports. By adhering to standards equivalent to the International Association of Classification Societies (IACS), we ensure that every vessel under our register meets the highest level of structural and operational integrity.</p><h3>Why Choose Girik Class?</h3><ul><li><strong>Digital-First Approach:</strong> Real-time certificate verification and seamless online survey scheduling.</li><li><strong>Global Network:</strong> Expert surveyors available 24/7 in strategic maritime hubs.</li><li><strong>Regulatory Authorization:</strong> Authorized by multiple flag administrations to perform statutory inspections.</li><li><strong>Transparent Lifecycle:</strong> Intelligent tracking from job assignment to finalized certification.</li></ul><p>At Girik Class, we don\'t just inspect; we partner with shipowners and management companies to ensure compliance is a smooth, efficient, and auditable process.</p>\", \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-04T09:17:58.000Z\", \"faq_items\": null, \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-04T10:35:51.000Z\", \"updated_by\": \"019c79a4-3eee-731a-9eff-b0eed303e215\", \"content_type\": \"PAGE\", \"is_published\": true, \"published_at\": \"2026-04-04T00:00:00.000Z\", \"thumbnail_url\": \"\"}','{\"id\": \"a1690e89-c30b-4bd2-a093-dbba6f686c04\", \"slug\": \"about-us\", \"title\": \"About Girik Class – Excellence in Maritime Classification\", \"body_html\": \"<h1>ABOUT US</h1><h2>Introduction</h2><p>GR Class is a modern maritime classification society committed to delivering reliable, efficient, and technology-driven solutions for vessel classification, certification, and regulatory compliance. The organization operates with a strong focus on safety, transparency, and global standards, supporting the maritime industry in meeting increasingly complex regulatory requirements.</p><p>GR Class combines deep domain expertise with advanced digital infrastructure to simplify compliance processes and enhance operational efficiency for ship owners, operators, and maritime stakeholders worldwide.</p><h2>Vision</h2><p>To establish a globally trusted and digitally enabled maritime ecosystem where compliance processes are seamless, transparent, and universally verifiable.</p><h2>Mission</h2><p>GR Class is dedicated to:</p><ul><li>Providing accurate and reliable classification and certification services</li><li>Enhancing maritime safety through strict adherence to international standards</li><li>Integrating modern technology into traditional maritime processes</li><li>Delivering efficient, transparent, and accessible compliance solutions</li><li>Building long-term relationships based on trust, integrity, and performance</li></ul><h2>Organizational Expertise</h2><p>GR Class is supported by a team of qualified marine surveyors, engineers, and compliance specialists with extensive industry experience. The organization maintains a strong operational framework that ensures consistent service delivery across different regions and jurisdictions.</p><p>The team is equipped to handle a wide range of technical assessments, inspections, and audits, ensuring that vessels meet all applicable international conventions and regulatory requirements.</p><h2>Global Operations</h2><p>GR Class operates across multiple geographical regions, providing services through a network of experienced professionals and strategic partnerships. This global presence enables:</p><ul><li>Timely inspection and certification services</li><li>Consistent application of international standards</li><li>Efficient coordination with maritime authorities and stakeholders</li><li>Continuous support for clients operating across different jurisdictions</li></ul><h2>Core Services</h2><h3>Classification Services</h3><p>GR Class provides vessel classification based on structural integrity, safety standards, and operational performance. These services ensure that vessels meet established technical criteria throughout their lifecycle.</p><h3>Statutory Certification</h3><p>The organization issues statutory certificates in compliance with international maritime conventions and flag state requirements, ensuring legal and operational readiness of vessels.</p><h3>Surveys and Inspections</h3><p>Comprehensive surveys and inspections are conducted to verify compliance with safety, environmental, and operational standards. These include periodic, renewal, and special surveys.</p><h3>Technical Advisory</h3><p>GR Class offers expert advisory services to support vessel design, modification, retrofitting, and compliance planning.</p><h3>Transfer of Class</h3><p>The organization facilitates the smooth transfer of vessels into its classification system, ensuring minimal disruption and full compliance continuity.</p><h2>Digital Transformation</h2><p>GR Class adopts a digital-first approach to maritime certification and compliance. The organization utilizes secure and scalable technologies to:</p><ul><li>Issue digitally verifiable certificates</li><li>Maintain centralized compliance records</li><li>Enable real-time access to certification data</li><li>Reduce dependency on manual documentation</li><li>Improve transparency and operational efficiency</li></ul><h2>Quality and Compliance Commitment</h2><p>Quality assurance is a fundamental aspect of GR Class operations. The organization follows strict internal and external standards to ensure the highest level of service delivery. This includes:</p><ul><li>Regular audits and performance evaluations</li><li>Continuous professional training and development</li><li>Implementation of internationally recognized best practices</li><li>Ongoing monitoring and improvement of operational processes</li></ul><h2>Core Values</h2><ul><li>Integrity: Maintaining transparency and ethical conduct in all operations</li><li>Reliability: Delivering consistent and dependable services</li><li>Innovation: Leveraging technology to improve efficiency and effectiveness</li><li>Safety: Prioritizing human life, environmental protection, and operational security</li><li>Excellence: Striving for the highest standards in all aspects of service delivery</li></ul><h2>Future Direction</h2><p>GR Class is focused on continuous growth and innovation. The organization aims to expand its global reach, enhance digital capabilities, and introduce advanced solutions that further streamline maritime compliance and certification processes.</p>\", \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-04T09:17:58.000Z\", \"faq_items\": null, \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-10T03:06:48.477Z\", \"updated_by\": \"019c79a4-3eee-731a-9eff-b0eed303e215\", \"content_type\": \"PAGE\", \"is_published\": true, \"published_at\": \"2026-04-04T00:00:00.000Z\", \"thumbnail_url\": \"\"}','::ffff:127.0.0.1','Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/146.0.0.0 Safari/537.36','2026-04-10 03:06:48','2026-04-10 03:06:48'),('1735530e-ac23-48a2-a572-b9408fa2b7c5','019c79a4-4930-71fd-aa73-887301791935','GENERATE_SIGNED_URL','File',NULL,NULL,'{\"key\": \"surveys/photos/0130e44a-4e1e-436a-ad86-923672de8ef4-attendance_1771955826673.jpg\", \"expires_in\": 3600}',NULL,NULL,'2026-02-24 17:57:07','2026-02-24 17:57:07'),('173c82d8-99ba-496e-a0ca-3494f7355c9c','019c79a4-4930-71fd-aa73-887301791935','GENERATE_SIGNED_URL','File',NULL,NULL,'{\"key\": \"documents/surveys/767e3331-fd07-4